"ai" does not express the shape of the hand wearing fingerless gloves. This is an unavoidable phenomenon.

You can modify the shape of the hand using the in-paint function, or you can print out a normal hand by excluding the fingerless gloves prompt.

I apologize if the example prompts seem long. But I take costume reproduction and quality very seriously.
